Add the ability to customize the header for the main portal & each project with custom links.

Use case: There is no way to add clear links for customers to other resources, like documentation and forums, even if those products are Atlassian products. We use Confluence and Questions and customized Confluence with custom links in the header for: Documentation, Questions, Support Tickets. We would like to have the ability to add links in the header on Service desk to link back to documentation and questions.

The ability to add custom text links to the header would solve this problem.

